        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lone Star Reimbursement Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Defense and the Department of Homeland Security to each provide $2.2 billion to the state of Texas as reimbursement for the costs of Operation Lone Star incurred in FY2022 and FY2023.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;(Operation Lone Star is a border security operation initiated and carried out by the state of Texas.) &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
